Raza Gull is the leader of this group of three members requesting 30,000 Afghani for the following business improvement goals:

Reza Gull wants to obtain a loan for her embroidery business; 
Habibia would like to receive a loan on behalf of her husband, a taxi driver; 
Jan Begam is requesting a loan for her husband's general store. 

All the group members express their grateful admiration for the Kiva process.
